  "detailed_description": "Burg Battle is a reverse tower defense game. Build custom bases, strategically counter your enemies, and push to destroy their castle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/ffde46b900d6741e5cba63505df1034a.poster.avif?t=1664892128\" width=500 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/ffde46b900d6741e5cba63505df1034a.webm?t=1664892128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/ffde46b900d6741e5cba63505df1034a.mp4?t=1664892128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play online with your friends or offline with bots.<br></li><li> Two game modes: traditional tug of war and horde.<br></li><li> A deep progression system where you can customize for your playstyle.<br></li><li> Two unique races to play, each with their own units, abilities, and talent trees.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/dbb0c1694dd7dd3f9dfeb00448a6d97b.poster.avif?t=1664892128\" width=500 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/dbb0c1694dd7dd3f9dfeb00448a6d97b.webm?t=1664892128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/dbb0c1694dd7dd3f9dfeb00448a6d97b.mp4?t=1664892128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Burg Battle is a reverse tower defense game. Build custom bases, strategically counter your enemies, and push to destroy their castle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/ffde46b900d6741e5cba63505df1034a.poster.avif?t=1664892128\" width=500 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/ffde46b900d6741e5cba63505df1034a.webm?t=1664892128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/ffde46b900d6741e5cba63505df1034a.mp4?t=1664892128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play online with your friends or offline with bots.<br></li><li> Two game modes: traditional tug of war and horde.<br></li><li> A deep progression system where you can customize for your playstyle.<br></li><li> Two unique races to play, each with their own units, abilities, and talent trees.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/dbb0c1694dd7dd3f9dfeb00448a6d97b.poster.avif?t=1664892128\" width=500 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/dbb0c1694dd7dd3f9dfeb00448a6d97b.webm?t=1664892128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447420/extras/dbb0c1694dd7dd3f9dfeb00448a6d97b.mp4?t=1664892128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
